title: Nothing has changed, Steve??
description:
Jalen & Jacoby dig into sound from a couple of media gatherings - but mainly: Steve Nash saying nothing's changed in Brooklyn, that he and KD had a 'moment' and it's over. Really? And DeAndre Ayton says he hasn't spoken with head coach Monty Williams since getting benched in Game 7. Really? The guys have THOUGHTS. Plus, an in depth breakdown of two best friend's phone etiquette. Hope you enjoy. One.
